Class Door

java.lang.Object
  Door

public class Door
extends java.lang.Object

Door.java Written By: Lauren Luo & Adrianna Valle Date:12-10-16 This class simulates a Door object in which it takes in a weight value, which corresponds to a designated key, a message when the door is locked and a message when the door is unlocked. Door locking/unlocking allows for another layer of fun for the player on top of the maze-like structure of our game. Note that a weight of 0 means the door is unlocked and no locked msg is present.
